commit.message:
auto merge of #11480 : SiegeLord/rust/float_base, r=cmr

This fixes the incorrect lexing of things like:

~~~rust
let b = 0o2f32;
let d = 0o4e6;
let f = 0o6e6f32;
~~~

and brings the float literal lexer in line with the description of the float literals in the manual.

